{"id": 3892, "title": "Ticket #3892: Make python-bindings more dictionary-friendly", "description": "<blockquote>\nRight now, the python bindings must receive a <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> object for several methods.  We should enhance them so a python dictionary is an acceptable shortcut.\n\n<p>Example before:\n\n</p><p></p><div class=\"verbatim\">\n<pre>import htcondor\nimport classad\nhtcondor.Schedd().submit(classad.ClassAd({\"Cmd\": \"/bin/echo\"}))\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Example after:\n\n</p><p></p><div class=\"verbatim\">\n<pre>import htcondor\nhtcondor.Schedd().submit({\"Cmd\": \"/bin/echo\"})\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>It's a small change, but does increase usability.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\nTicket is back in the docpending state, as it needs a version history item.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Oct-30 14:42</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/7e28e38ae4f523e320b72a37b6ef1f9a7e8f2d26\">[38029]</a></span>: place example use of dictionary where <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> would have been into examples within python bindings documentation <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3892\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3892'); return false;\" title=\"Make python-bindings more dictionary-friendly\">#3892</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Oct-30 13:05</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"